    public class Hackbots
extends IterativeRobot
implements ThreadsAndClasses
    The VM is configured to automatically run this class, and to call the functions corresponding to each mode, as described in the IterativeRobot documentation. If you change the name of this class or the package after creating this project, you must also update the manifest file in the resource directory. Main thread of the code, it starts all the threads in the beginning of enabling, as well as feeds the watchdog.
